                  <a href="./buy-form.php" class="btn">ORDER NOW</a>
                  <p class="main-property-title">DESCRIPTION:</p>
                  <p class="main-property-text">
                     Stay ahead of the pack with the AquaNomad Pro, the ultimate
                     water bottle for outdoor enthusiasts and athletes. This
                     bottle is designed to keep your drinks cold for 24 hours
                     thanks to our cutting-edge double-wall vacuum insulation.
                     The leakproof Chug Cap offers a controlled flow, making it
                     perfect for staying hydrated on the move.
                  </p>

                  <p class="main-property-title">KEY FEATURES:</p>
                  <ul>
                     <li class="main-property-text">
                        <bold>24 Hours Cold:</bold> Double-wall vacuum
                        insulation keeps your drinks icy cold for a full day.
                     </li>
                     <li class="main-property-text">
                        <bold>Leakproof Chug Cap:</bold> Conveniently sip
                        without spills – ideal for active lifestyles.
                     </li>
                     <li class="main-property-text">
                        <bold>Cupholder-Friendly:</bold> Designed to fit in most
                        cupholders, making it great for the car, gym, or trail.
                     </li>
                     <li class="main-property-text">
                        <bold>Pure Taste:</bold> Pro-grade stainless steel
                        ensures no flavor transfer, so you taste only what you
                        pour in.
                     </li>
                     <li class="main-property-text">
                        <bold>Dishwasher Safe:</bold> Clean your bottle
                        effortlessly by putting it into the dishwasher.
                     </li>
                  </ul>
